      "definition": "Typed deterministic Tool that writes JSON-LD entity files conforming to a given foundation schema.",
      "success_criterion": "Reuses the existing entity-emitter skill (task #58 in feedback log) — well-validated in production.",
      "depends_on": ["node:filesystem-integration"],
